data.description: Welcome to this charming well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1 1/2-bath ranch home in a 55+ community. Enjoy an open layout, spacious bedrooms, and a cozy fireplace in the winter months. Some of the highlights of the home include a brand-new roof, new water heater, a garage with a laundry area, and a large utility sink. The exterior of the home is equally well-maintained, with a landscaped yard and covered patio that offers a serene and private setting for outdoor enjoyment. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is conveniently situated near parks and shopping. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming move-in-ready ranch your home! Schedule a showing today!
